{"tid":1203511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人少啲狗就逐個聞，人多就再多狗都聞唔哂","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:02:19.000Z","uid":42364,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e8b2f466a1efa89d15e70373471795c297f980","tid":1203511,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8269f2c8dbbdf58116eba6da9f409e8503ba31fe","tid":1203511,"uid":199631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如遇狗，如何保護自已？<br />\n<br />\n事前：<br />\n建議留低以下資料比信得過嘅人：<br />\n- 中英文全名<br />\n- 身份證號碼<br />\n- 年齡<br />\n<br />\n行裝：<br />\n- 警察有權check bag ，但冇權沒收物品， 亦唔需要解釋用途<br />\n- 除非被拘捕 電話不用交出<br />\n- 危險性攻擊性物品不要放在身上或背包上（如：萬用刀、火機、鉸剪及𠝹刀）<br />\n- 警察的問題除了姓名、 職業 、住邊區之外 其他任何問題都唔答<br />\n- 不回答問題不是阻差 ，是個人權利<br />\n- 警察有權取看身份證 ，但無權沒收<br />\n- 在任何情況下電話不用解鎖、冇權要求開電話或交出密碼<br />\n<br />\n如被拘捕:<br />\n- 可以不簽署任何文件<br />\n- 有權致電律師和家人（不限次數）<br />\n<br />\n搜身：<br />\n  -搜身不需除衫，只需除褸<br />\n  -只有女警可以搜女生身<br />\n  *若搜身期間受到侵犯或性騷擾（包括言語上），記低時間和搜查者編號告知律師"},{"pid":"dc66ce6ef97d06538cfedbb41708a2727d7a2784","tid":1203511,"uid":42364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"冇乜裝備人生又冇乜包袱既<br />\n試下挑釁到差佬講要搭你返狗屋<br />\n佢地搭一個人比查一個人既人力同功夫多好多"},{"pid":"a1a41929e8c5f7da62c1cc3131f532d7f36ffadf","tid":1203511,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"戰火已經點燃!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! <br />\n人海戰術反包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a1d9df861a3f7ca2d54505258dfc57890e4cc3","tid":1203511,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"越draw得走越多警力越好"},{"pid":"27b11b77927f67911aa5320b1c5af014a45ff8b3","tid":1203511,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"去其他站反而分散哂<br />\n佢地灣仔中環都會有狗<br />\n分散令到自己同其他義工更加大機會畀人抄"},{"pid":"3c737d9669f4f5c991bdbf555d229f1f9bede7b9","tid":1203511,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"趁班狗畀記者圍住影緊<br />\n拿拿聲金鐘出"},{"pid":"e4515e78bacf48070c18529521f7f02a91424e44","tid":1203511,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"多謝記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}